high_descs: Turn right and head across the room to the sink that is to left left of the fridge
Pick up the potato that is sitting in front of the sink
Take a step to the left and stand directly in front of the sink
Place the potato inside the sink
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle that is sitting inside the sink
Slice the potato
Place the knife into the sink
Pick up a slice of the potato that is inside the sink
Turn to your left and face the microwave
Open the microwave and place the potato slice inside to the right of the tomato then close the door and turn it on. Open the microwave and pick up the potato slice and then close the door.
Turn to your right and face the sink
Place the potato slice into the sink to the left of the knife
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked potato in a sink

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room to face the sink.
Pick up the potato on the edge of the sink.
Step to the left and look up to face the sink.
Place the potato in the left side of the sink.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Cut the potato in the sink into slices.
Place the knife in the sink.
Pick up a potato slice from in the sink.
Turn to the left to face the microwave.
Heat the potato slice in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn to the right to face the sink.
Place the potato slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To heat a slice of potato and place it in the sink.

high_descs: turn around to the right go forward turn right towards the sink
pick up the potato from the sink
turn to the left go forward towards the sink
put the potato on the sink
pick up the knife from the sink
slice the potato that is inside the sink
pick up a slice of the potato
turn to the left towards the microwave
open the microwave door put the slice inside the microwave
heat up the slice of potato in the microwave
get it back out turn to the right towards the sink
put the slice inside the sink
anns.task_desc: put a heated slice of a potato inside the sink
